  "status": "Final",
  "summary": "This EIP proposes an extension to the [ERC-721](./eip-721.md) standard for Non-Fungible Tokens (NFTs) to enable multi-redeemable NFTs. Redemption provides a means for NFT holders to demonstrate ownership and eligibility of their NFT, which in turn enables them to receive a physical or digital item. This extension would allow an NFT to be redeemed in multiple scenarios and maintain a record of its redemption status on the blockchain.",
  "title": "Multi-redeemable NFTs"
